cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the problem of hand pose estimation using a single RGB camera. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The method involves real-time estimation, which suggests the involvement of robotics and control, hence cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with 3D pose estimation, which could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics).
